description: How to create an ACF-driven Gutenberg block in this theme. Apply when creating, building, or scaffolding a Gutenberg/ACF/"digiway" block from a Figma link or an image.
globs: ["template-parts/gutenberg-blocks/**", "acf-json/**"]
alwaysApply: false
